Class ModelLink

  • java.lang.Object
    • tech.cae.jsdf.v1_7.ModelLink
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SDFType

    @JsonClassDescription(value="A physical link with inertia, collision, and visual properties. A link must be a child of a model, and any number of links may exist in a model.")
public final class ModelLink
extends Object
implements SDFType
    A physical link with inertia, collision, and visual properties. A link must be a child of a model, and any number of links may exist in a model.
